I will not rate this recipe as I made a few changes. I do feel that this recipe is quite forgiving in that area. I could not find verjus so I used a Muscatel vinegar. The honey disappeared from the cabinet so I used blue agave sweetener (I believe honey would have added more depth)and I don't care for hazelnuts so I used pecan. All that being said, it was a delicious salad. Do not be tempted to sweeten the dressing, the honey (or in my case agave) will offset the tartness.

